    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You fell in here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they made an appel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all did 120 girls, and then he selected me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Jewish was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Burgermeister. ?] He was in charge of the-- there was 3,000 men and 120 girls then, when I was there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he select 10 girls for the office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there are nine now, with the 10th [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means in Polish, please, I want to go to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I knew that everybody was telling them if I go to an office, I wouldn't have anything, because those girls are single, and I knew I had my father there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told them the only way I can help is this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I used to send my daddy-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Excuse me for interrupting, I change the subject.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was still home, when they grabbed Daddy, we used to-- before even we sent packages to my brother for short time, they were able-- we were able to correspond and send some packages, which we did to help.",
